# Testing and validation

Use package scripts based on the touched surface:

```powershell
npm run type-check
npm run build
npm run dev
npm run upload
```

For moderation behavior, validate safe-mode defaults, audit-log writes, idempotency keys, cooldowns, and target action routing.
For upload/publish work, preserve the automation and verify the Devvit command output rather than replacing it with manual steps.
